<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śākābdē ratnanāgagrahapatigaṇitē māsicāṣāḍa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>saṁjñē sa pamyāṁ bhānuvārē hariśikharipatēragratō dīpadī
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ptyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhāradvājānvayōdādhakhilavibhavasaṁsiddhayē bhīma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nākhya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> paṁcāśat(k) <unclear>gāḥ</unclear> pratidinamurudhīrbhīmanāmā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>tyaputraḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavaru(r)ṣaṁbulu 1288 gunēṁṭi puṣya pu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nnamayu Ādivāramunāṁḍu sōmagravāṇakālamaṁdu <unclear>jatu</unclear>rvē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>di guḍḍayapegaḍa bhīmanapegaḍaṁgāri koḍuku bhīmana tana
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ku Iṣṭartthasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuni sannidini nitya
<lb n="9" break="no"/>munnu Oka Ākhaṁḍadīpamu veluṁguṭaku kūnupilli ko
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍuku gōrayavasamunaṁ beṭṭina mōdālu 50 Ītanikini 
<lb n="11"/>sā dhōvarāna ceṟuvuvenaka paṁduyi polamu 10 peṭṭe
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nu Ī guraya nelapaḍi Ēḍu kuṁcālu 7 neyi decci bhaṁḍā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>rānaṁ beṭaṁgalāṁḍu Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

